           <h2> General Rules:</h2>
       <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Only 2 participants are allowed per college.</li>
                    <li>Preliminary Round: 2-minute duration with no karaoke permitted, (online.)</li>
                    <li>Showcase Round: Stage performance duration is set at 3-4 minutes. </li>
                        <li>Participants are allowed to bring either track or accompanist(limit: 1)</li>
