                <h2>Round 1 Rules:</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>This is an elimination round.</li>
                    <li>The participants have to send a recorded video. The duration of the video should not exceed the time limit of 3 Minutes.</li>
                    <li>Participants must rename their video as - Name_CollegeName_ContactNo. </li>
                    <li>The Participants will be judged on the basis of their recorded videos. </li>
                    <li>Video Submission deadline- 26 February 2024 till 11:59 pm.</li>
                    <li>The video should be sent to the respective coordinator's Whatsapp number.</li>
                    <li>Voice clarity should be there in the video and it should be recorded in one go. </li>
                    <li>Any kind of voiceover will not be allowed. </li>
                    <li>Background music not allowed, but participants can use their own instrument while singing.</li>

                    <li>The results for this round will be shared via event's Whatsapp Group.
                </ul>
                </p>

                <h2>Final round Rules:</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Showcase Round Selected participants from round 1 will proceed to the second round which will be conducted in college campus.</li>
